    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         Test Procedure for NEPA_CEScreeningIP
         Validates the DetermineRecommendation Set Values formula logic across
         all six boundary conditions defined by 40 CFR 1501.4 acreage thresholds
         and the extraordinary circumstances flag.

         Each test block:
           1. Sets mock input values
           2. Calls NEPA_CEScreeningIP
           3. Asserts the expected Recommendation output

         Per OMB M-25-21: these are heuristic pre-screening thresholds only.
         The authoritative CE determination is made by a human NEPA coordinator.
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

